# cue:managed-ignore
# Transient Cue runtime files (sessions, state, logs, search cache)
# Memory (.cue/memory/) is NOT ignored — it is a tracked live doc whose mutations
# flow through the auto-commit pipeline (cue-memory-auto-commit.ts) so dev never
# carries raw memory dirty state. The whole .cue/search/ dir (incl. index.yml) IS
# ignored — index.yml is regenerated each boot with machine-specific paths.
# Connected memory DB is gitignored (binary — re-derivable from JSONL evidence sidecar)
.cue/states/
.cue/ports/
.cue/sessions/
.cue/logs/
.cue/ralph-status/
.cue/search/
.cue/state.json
.cue/port
.cue/ralph-loop-status.md
.cue/ralph-recovery.json
.cue/watchdog-prompt.txt
.cue/watchdog-prompt.txt.tmp
.cue/watchdog-trigger
.cue/watchdog-trigger.tmp
.cue/*.pid
.cue/**/*.pid
.cue/soul-meta.json
.cue/engagement/
.cue/insights-evidence-*.jsonl
.cue/temple/temple-brain.db
.cue/temple/temple-brain.db-wal
.cue/temple/temple-brain.db-shm
